variables.name: RELATION_TO_MEAL_UNKNOWN

variables.name: RELATION_TO_MEAL_GENERAL

variables.name: RELATION_TO_MEAL_FASTING
variables.comment: Reading was taken during a fasting period.

variables.name: RELATION_TO_MEAL_BEFORE_MEAL
variables.comment: Reading was taken before an unspecified meal.

variables.name: RELATION_TO_MEAL_AFTER_MEAL
variables.comment: Reading was taken after an unspecified meal.
